metadata.name: Regular Monday
metadata.description:
It just a regular monday, business as usual.

This is NiftyMonki first piece on Foundation and the first for Monday Monday Monday collection, which is probably about Monday.

Pixel art perfect loop, 32 frames at 12 fps.

Hand-pixeled in 300x300, carefully upscaled to 1200x1200 gif.

Done entirely in photoshop using only mouse.
